told
> me that the carsales from their dealership slowed down very much, so
> bussiness is going bad, not a isolated case as it seems to be all over
> Germany, so they do not have a too large pressure from VW of Germany, but
> like a good manager he is focussing on his bussiness now and not much on
the
> show, he even told me when he should decide now he would cancel the show,
> but officially he only take his decission around the New Year, he hopes
> bussiness become better by that time so he got a little spare time for
> organising the show, the problem is mainly with permissions, reservations
> and all the work that has to be done long time before the event, as there
> are already many people who offered him help around the weekend....
>
> Anyway so plse preview that there is a 50% change Bad Camberg will not be
